## Data Attribution

This application uses wine and food pairing data from various sources:
- Wine review data courtesy of wine enthusiasts and professionals
- Food pairing recommendations from culinary experts
- Price and rating information from wine databases

Please respect the original data sources and use this application for 
educational and personal purposes.